      <title>斯卡拉穆奇预测，美联储降息和美国规则趋于清晰将推动比特币价格创下新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/scaramucci-expects-bitcoin-btc-record-on-rate-cuts-clearer-us-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对冲基金经理安东尼·斯卡拉穆奇 (Anthony Scaramucci) 预测，受降息和 11 月总统大选后美国加密货币监管明晰化的双重推动，比特币将创下历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/scaramucci-expects-bitcoin-btc-record-on-rate-cuts-clearer-us-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 05:38:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储降息是亚洲各国央行行动的发令枪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/fed-cut-to-serve-as-starting-gun-for-central-banks-across-asia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储将至少下调利率四分之一个百分点，亚洲各国央行在经历了两年多的货币困境后终于松了一口气。不过，该地区货币政策的未来之路仍将坎坷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/fed-cut-to-serve-as-starting-gun-for-central-banks-across-asia</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
